  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add sliced onion and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, red bell pepper, and cook for another 2 minutes until slightly softened.",
    "Add sliced olives and diced tomatoes, and cook until tomatoes start to break down, about 5 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle oregano, paprika, salt, and pepper; stir to combine.",
    "Pour in lemon juice and cook for 2 minutes, allowing the flavors to meld.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and let the mixture simmer for 8 minutes to develop a rich, fragrant sauce.",
    "Remove from heat, stir in fresh parsley if using, and serve warm straight from the skillet."
  ],
